translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショーの優勝者に魔軍の館に来させ魔物大将軍様相手に１晩ショーをさせる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner of the girls' show is brought to the Demon Army's mansion to perform a show for one night before the Demon Great General.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優勝者とその関係者は町からの出入りが自由となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner and their associates are given free passage in and out of the town.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ひどい状況になった、自分の彼女や娘を調教し、大会で優勝して身の安全を図ろうとする連中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The situation has become terrible—people train their own girlfriends or daughters to win the tournament as a way to secure their safety.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 実際には元々ガールズショーに参加していたプロが優勝を続けているのだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In reality, the professionals who originally participated in the girls' show continue to win.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかたがないんです・・これをリーザスへの裏切りと言うのでしたら、魔軍を助けて下さいと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can't be helped... If you call this a betrayal to Leazas, then please help the Demon Army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その為に俺様が来たのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's why I came here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よし、今回は俺様が参加するぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, this time I'll participate myself.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい？リーザス軍が助けに来てくれるのでは？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Won't the Leazas army come to help?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは後だ、まずは俺様がガールショーに優勝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That comes later, first I have to win the girls' show.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスさんが優勝して魔物大将軍に近づき倒す、これが作戦です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The plan is for Rance to win, approach the Demon Great General, and defeat him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・そうですか、わかりました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...I see, understood.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大会の方は我々の方で優勝できるように手配します
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll arrange things so that you can win the tournament.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫です、審査員は全てこちら側なので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't worry, all the judges are on our side.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Choice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　それで頼む
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Then, I'm counting on you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　まて、正々堂々と優勝する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Wait, let's win fair and square.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ※こちらは簡易ルートです。イベントは少なめで
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *This is a simplified route. Fewer events.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショー当日
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The day of the girls' show.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 舞台裏、専用衣装のチルディとランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Backstage, Childi and Rance in their special costumes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫お前なら出来る、堂々といつもの通りにやれ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's okay, you can do it. Be confident and do it as usual.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい、コーチ、がんばります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, coach, I'll do my best.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・そして幕があがった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...And then the curtain rose.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: チルディよりプロの調教師が出した女の子の方が遙かに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The girl produced by the professional trainer was far more...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エロかったが、俺のチルディが優勝した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: erotic, but my Childi won.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、裏で票操作しているからあたりまえだがな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, it's obvious since the votes were rigged behind the scenes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: チルディは知らずによろこんでいた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Childi was happy, unaware of this.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 選択：正々堂々を選んだ時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Choice: When choosing to win fair and square.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まて、不正はよくない、それに俺が調教したチルディは完璧だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wait, cheating is no good, besides, the Childi I trained is perfect.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんな事はしなくても優勝だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We can win without doing something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし・・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今回参加している調教師にＸＸＸがいました、彼は前回の優勝者ですごい人です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Among the trainers participating this time was XXX, the previous champion and an incredible person.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とても素人の方が・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A complete amateur couldn't...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シャラップ、俺は天才だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shut up, I'm a genius.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショーが始まった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The girls' show has begun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アナウンサー　適当に誰か　何故かオーロラでも良し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Announcer: Someone random, for some reason Aurora is fine too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背景は天井とかでごまかして、専用ないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The background is faked with a ceiling or such; there is no dedicated one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 調教師ＸＸＸが作り上げた穴奴隷が出る（立ち絵　穴奴隷２）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The hole slave created by trainer XXX appears (standing illustration: hole slave 2).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何かすごい所を見せる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She shows something amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 次にチルディ（立ち絵　チルディ／調教衣装）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Next is Childi (standing illustration: Childi / training outfit).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: つたないががんばる、恥ずかしがりながらがんばる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She's clumsy but tries her best, working hard while embarrassed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たくさんに見られているという事で我を忘れてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She loses herself because she is being watched by many.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何か事故的な事があり、それが観客に大受け
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Something accidental happens, and it becomes a big hit with the audience.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 観客は全て魔物兵、魔物将軍、ヨシフはいません。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: All the audience are demon soldiers and demon generals; Yoshif is not present.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優勝は・・投票結果、チルディ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner... by voting results, is Childi.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やったぜ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We did it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショーが始まった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The girls' show has begun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アナウンサー　適当に誰か　何故かオーロラでも良し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Announcer: Someone random, for some reason Aurora is fine.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背景は天井とかでごまかして、専用ないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The background is faked with a ceiling or something; there is no dedicated one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 調教師ＸＸＸが作り上げた穴奴隷が出る（立ち絵　穴奴隷２）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The hole slave created by trainer XXX appears (standing illustration: hole slave 2).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何かすごい所を見せる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She shows something amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 次にチルディ（立ち絵　チルディ／調教衣装）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Next is Childi (standing illustration: Childi / training outfit).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 完全に駄目、つたない・・エロさが足りない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Completely no good, clumsy... lacks eroticism.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 観客にびびって萎縮して興奮なんて出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She is intimidated by the audience, shrinking and unable to get excited.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 完全な負けだった・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a complete loss...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優勝は　相手の穴奴隷
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner is the opponent's hole slave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その後、リーザス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After that, Leazas Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショーの優勝者に魔軍の館に来させ魔物大将軍様相手に１晩ショーをさせる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner of the girls' show is brought to the Demon Army's mansion to perform a show for one night before the Demon Great General.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優勝者とその関係者は町からの出入りが自由となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner and their associates are given free passage in and out of the town.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ひどい状況になった、自分の彼女や娘を調教し、大会で優勝して身の安全を図ろうとする連中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The situation has become terrible—people train their own girlfriends or daughters to win the tournament as a way to secure their safety.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 実際には元々ガールズショーに参加していたプロが優勝を続けているのだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In reality, the professionals who originally participated in the girls' show continue to win.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかたがないんです・・これをリーザスへの裏切りと言うのでしたら、魔軍を助けて下さいと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can't be helped... If you call this a betrayal to Leazas, then please help the Demon Army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その為に俺様が来たのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's why I came here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よし、今回は俺様が参加するぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, this time I'll participate myself.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい？リーザス軍が助けに来てくれるのでは？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Won't the Leazas army come to help?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは後だ、まずは俺様がガールショーに優勝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That comes later, first I have to win the girls' show.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスさんが優勝して魔物大将軍に近づき倒す、これが作戦です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The plan is for Rance to win, approach the Demon Great General, and defeat him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・そうですか、わかりました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...I see, understood.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大会の方は我々の方で優勝できるように手配します
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll arrange things so that you can win the tournament.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫です、審査員は全てこちら側なので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't worry, all the judges are on our side.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Choice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　それで頼む
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Then, I'm counting on you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　まて、正々堂々と優勝する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Wait, let's win fair and square.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ※こちらは簡易ルートです。イベントは少なめで
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *This is a simplified route. Fewer events.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショー当日
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The day of the girls' show.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 舞台裏、専用衣装のチルディとランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Backstage, Childi and Rance in their special costumes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫お前なら出来る、堂々といつもの通りにやれ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's okay, you can do it. Be confident and do it as usual.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい、コーチ、がんばります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, coach, I'll do my best.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・そして幕があがった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...And then the curtain rose.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: チルディよりプロの調教師が出した女の子の方が遙かに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The girl produced by the professional trainer was far more...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エロかったが、俺のチルディが優勝した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: erotic, but my Childi won.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、裏で票操作しているからあたりまえだがな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, it's obvious since the votes were rigged behind the scenes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: チルディは知らずによろこんでいた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Childi was happy, unaware of this.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 選択：正々堂々を選んだ時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Choice: When choosing to win fair and square.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まて、不正はよくない、それに俺が調教したチルディは完璧だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wait, cheating is no good, besides, the Childi I trained is perfect.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんな事はしなくても優勝だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We can win without doing something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし・・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今回参加している調教師にＸＸＸがいました、彼は前回の優勝者ですごい人です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Among the trainers participating this time was XXX, the previous champion and an incredible person.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とても素人の方が・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A complete amateur couldn't...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シャラップ、俺は天才だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shut up, I'm a genius.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショーが始まった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The girls' show has begun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アナウンサー　適当に誰か　何故かオーロラでも良し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Announcer: Someone random, for some reason Aurora is fine too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背景は天井とかでごまかして、専用ないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The background is faked with a ceiling or such; there is no dedicated one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 調教師ＸＸＸが作り上げた穴奴隷が出る（立ち絵　穴奴隷２）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The hole slave created by trainer XXX appears (standing illustration: hole slave 2).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何かすごい所を見せる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She shows something amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 次にチルディ（立ち絵　チルディ／調教衣装）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Next is Childi (standing illustration: Childi / training outfit).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: つたないががんばる、恥ずかしがりながらがんばる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She's clumsy but tries her best, working hard while embarrassed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たくさんに見られているという事で我を忘れてしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She loses herself because she is being watched by many.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何か事故的な事があり、それが観客に大受け
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Something accidental happens, and it becomes a big hit with the audience.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 観客は全て魔物兵、魔物将軍、ヨシフはいません。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: All the audience are demon soldiers and demon generals; Yoshif is not present.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優勝は・・投票結果、チルディ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner... by voting results, is Childi.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やったぜ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We did it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガールズショーが始まった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The girls' show has begun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アナウンサー　適当に誰か　何故かオーロラでも良し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Announcer: Someone random, for some reason Aurora is fine.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背景は天井とかでごまかして、専用ないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The background is faked with a ceiling or something; there is no dedicated one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 調教師ＸＸＸが作り上げた穴奴隷が出る（立ち絵　穴奴隷２）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The hole slave created by trainer XXX appears (standing illustration: hole slave 2).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何かすごい所を見せる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She shows something amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 次にチルディ（立ち絵　チルディ／調教衣装）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Next is Childi (standing illustration: Childi / training outfit).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 完全に駄目、つたない・・エロさが足りない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Completely no good, clumsy... lacks eroticism.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 観客にびびって萎縮して興奮なんて出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She is intimidated by the audience, shrinking and unable to get excited.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 完全な負けだった・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a complete loss...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優勝は　相手の穴奴隷
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The winner is the opponent's hole slave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その後、リーザス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After that, Leazas Castle.
